quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,1,"Alif,\tLaam,\tMiiym.\t(Insiguro\tyizi\tndome\thamwe\tn’uwufise\tubumenyi bwazo n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  3,2,"Imana ntayindi\titegerezwa gusengwa\tbimwe\tvy’ukuri\tatariyo yonyene gusa, ikaba ariyo iyobora ibintu vyose"
  3,3,"Niyo yabamanuriye igitabu bimwe vy’ukuri cemeza ivyabaye imbere yiwe, nayo niyo yamanuye igitabu ca Taurati hamwe n’igitabu c’Injili"
  3,4,"Aho hambere kugira ngo habe uburongozi ku bantu Imana yaciye imanura ibindi\tbitabu\tvy’ugutandukanya\thagati\ty’ukuri\tn’ibinyoma,\tmu\tvy’ukuri bamwe bahakanye aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu bazoba bafise ibihano bikaze cane, n’Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi bukwiye hamwe n’ukwihora"
  3,5,Ntankeka ku Mana ntacinyegeza icarico cose kibaho haba ng’aha kw’isi canke mw’Ijuru
  3,6,"Niyo ibagirira amashusho mukiri mumbanyi nkuko ibishaka, kandi ntawundi asengwa atari Imana yonyene rudende gusa, kuko niyo yonyene ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  3,7,"Niyo yabamanuriye igitabu murico harimwo amajambo y’Imana yoroshe mukwumvikana kwayo kandi ukaba ariwo mushingi w’intango w’ico gitabu ceranda, hakaba hariho n’ayandi majambo y’Imana matagatifu agomba gusa n’ayandi, na bamwe mu mitima yabo harimwo ubuzimire bagakurikira bimwe bifise amakenga kugira ngo bonone abantu n’ukumenya ukuri kwavyo ingene kumeze, kandi ntan’umwe azi uko kuri ingene kumeze atari Imana yonyene gusa, na bamwe bagize ubushaka shatsi bw’ubumenyi bama bavuga abati:- twebwe turavyemeye yuko vyose bivuye ku Mana yacu, mugabo ntibibuka atari abafise ubwenge"
  3,8,"Muremyi wacu ntutakaze imitima yacu mugihe wamaze kuturongora, kandi uduhe n’imihezagiro ivuye kuri wewe, mu vy’ukuri ni wewe mutanzi mukuru"
  3,9,"Muremyi wacu, ni wewe uzokoranya abantu bose kuri wa musi udafise amakenga, mu vy’ukuri Imana ntita indagano yayo"